# Changelog for lovinsp

## v1.3.0 - 2025-12-27
- Fix: API 名称从 `LovinspPlugin` 改为 `lovinspPlugin`（小写开头）
- Fix: Next.js Turbopack 配置改为 `rules: lovinspPlugin({ bundler: 'turbopack' })`
- Add: 分开 Next.js Turbopack 和 Webpack 两种配置示例

## v1.2.0
- Initial tracked version
- Support Vite, Webpack, Next.js, Nuxt
- Auto-migrate from code-inspector

